messages.messageBody:
>"And, besides, I'll insruct you like me to entwine
>"The Myrtle of Venus with Bacchus's Vine.

Oh my...Too much drinking might prevent the vigorous
entwining of Bacchus' vine with anything.

>"The YELLOW-HAIRED GOD and his nine lusty Maids
>"From Helicon's Banks will incontinent flee,

Are the lusty maids and their god fleeing from their
own incontinence (a : failure to restrain sexual
appetite : UNCHASTITY b : inability of the body to
control the evacuative functions) Or are the maids
fleeing from their god's incontinence, or are they
fleeing in search of balm for their passions?
hmmmm...

>"I'll trim the young Dogs, for thus daring to twine
>"The Myrtle of VENUS with BACCUS'S Vine.

I hope the trimming is not of the Bobbit variety...

Nanci K.
